<section id="content">

<a href="http://sivers.org/"><img src="/css/DerekSivers-20141119-200.jpg"></a>
<p>
My name is Derek Sivers.
</p><p>
I've been a musician since 1984, and a professional musician for 13 years.
</p><p>
ln 1998 I created cdbaby.com and hostbaby.com
</p><p>
In 1999 I created musicthoughts.com because I loved how these thoughts from other musicians, about making music, would inspire me when making my own music.
</p><p>
You can also join the <a href="https://groups.yahoo.com/neo/groups/musicthoughts/info">musicthoughts email list</a> to talk with other musicians.
</p><p>
musicthoughts.com is a totally free non-commerical site, here only for your inspiration.
</p><p>
If you have an idea for what else it could be, please <a href="http://sivers.org/#follow">contact me</a>.
</p><p>
All of my new projects are at <a href="http://sivers.org/">sivers.org</a>
</p>

</section>

